<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-88-0063 </DOCNO><TEXT>The device includes particle conversion means into electrons, a microchannelplate set to amplify the election flux by electron multiplication, anelectroluminescent screen coupled to a set of optical fibers collectingthe luminous photons on the screen, a matrix of photosensitive diodes,and a digitalization and memorization device of signals given by thediodes.</TEXT></DOC>